OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRespite care: 'Burnt-out'  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmum says respite shortage  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Faffecting her family       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Some families in Northern Ireland are  
OL,6, on the edge of placing their children  
OL,7, into care due to the lack of respite   
OL,8, services, a children's rights lawyer   
OL,9, has said.                              
OL,11,FRespite care is provided by the health 
OL,12,Ftrusts for the parents of children with
OL,13,Fadditional needs.                      
OL,15,FIt allows parents or carers to take a  
OL,16,Fbreak from caring and have their       
OL,17,Fchildren looked after overnight.       
OL,19,FShort-term services have been reduced, 
OL,20,Fthe trusts have confirmed.             
